cost: variable cost to grow this crop
costCont: variable cost to grow this crop in a second and subsequent year
IEprevcrop: crop effect on subsequent disease incidence: 1 is max, 0 is no disease
DEcrop: average effect of disease on this crop
weedsurvival: proportion of weeds that survive to set seed
weedseedreturn: proportion of weed seeds returned to seedbank
label: label for plots
hide: if 'y' then not included in analysis for now
